DOMA. Don’t Ask Don’t Tell. Obergefell. The Respect for Marriage Act.

We’ve spent decades debating a simple question: should we as a country give equal rights to LGBTQ+ people? The answer is yes.

@POTUS just signed the Respect for Marriage Act, and I was honored to be there. https://t.co/IRfdoTg8Qr

